summary: This document pertains to a review of a Top Secret study regarding the examination of the bona fides of KGB defector Yuriy I. NOSENKO, dated February 1968. It includes deletions of certain portions containing information related to the security of ongoing CIA operations. The document requests the return of the study and related annexes upon completion of the review.
title: 2025 RELEASE UNDER THE PRESIDENT JOHN F. KENNEDY ASSASSINATION RECORDS ACT OF 1992
